name: Are You For Real? - The Carnivores' Dinner Party
description:
A wolf, a cat, a dog, a boar and a bear sit down for a meaty stew. The trade off is that they have to listen to Wolf tell his offensive stories. Where will the line be drawn?

4000 x 4000 pixels
2021
